{"tid":1830815,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際研究機構調查指 港警可靠度居第6勝美國","createTime":"2020-01-20T02:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T15:39:51.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf72bcab8ee4983ada251e6d48f71982e0d3643","tid":1830815,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"整體人類自由指數，香港以8.81分排行第三。<br />\n<br />\n警隊官方網頁上載了加拿大菲沙研究所就世界各地「警察可靠度」的評分與排名表，2019年調查結果顯示香港取得約8.9分，排名上升至第6，僅次於居首的芬蘭、瑞士、新加坡、冰島和紐西蘭，18年調查則排第8，美國在19年則獲約82分。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸昨在社交網站引用該資料發文，說要「祝賀香港警察」。至於菲沙研究所19年整體人類自由指數，香港以8.81分排行第三，僅次於紐西蘭與瑞士，加拿大已在香港之後排第4，美國只排第15。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/20200119_CR_%E8%8F%B2%E6%B2%99%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%89%801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F20200119_CR_%25E8%258F%25B2%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%2589%25801.jpg&h=39d2c51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警隊官方網頁上載了加拿大菲沙研究所就世界各地「警察可靠度」的評分與排名表。警隊官方網頁截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/01/20200119-CR-%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F01%2F20200119-CR-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A61.jpg&h=f3347bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菲沙研究所自2008年起每年發布「全球人類自由指數」，該指數以76種個人和經濟自由指標，就一系列的人類自由程度評分，「警察可靠度」就屬於「經濟自由」下「法制與產權」的其中一項指標，該評分的資料來源是世界經濟論壇的《世界競爭力報告書》。2019年的指數，是按共162個國家或地區於2017年的情況作評估。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/10/20191029_PO_%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F10%2F20191029_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A52.jpg&h=6b86312e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警隊同樣上載了世界經濟論壇《世界競爭力報告書》中，有關「警察服務可靠度」的評分。資料顯示，1.6萬名商界領袖於去年1至4月受訪，就各地的警察服務可靠度，以1分最低、7分最高作評分。結果香港取得6.4分，於141個經濟體中排名第6，排在芬蘭、新加坡、瑞士、冰島和巴林之後，美國亦是20大不入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/10/20190202_cr_%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F10%2F20190202_cr_%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A_FB.jpg&h=f0dc5582&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"011f4941f338baeedfec5c1e75a878df5d77fbc5","tid":1830815,"uid":19566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是按共162個國家或地區於2017年的情況作評估</blockquote>"},{"pid":"946e9f2f0dcf80ad344a7bc79ff2b761dc37d37f","tid":1830815,"uid":19321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"引用2017"},{"pid":"83c9ffce1ce7a63943ad13fc77638be3656d8127","tid":1830815,"uid":15300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"資料顯示，1.6萬名商界領袖於去年1至4月受訪，就各地的警察服務可靠度，以1分最低、7分最高作評分。<br />\n<br />\n又係小圈子打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cd9a45cdcf6abc6e70c7385b1cd6948cebd5a0","tid":1830815,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:20:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">按共162個國家或地區於2017年的情況作評估</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"118749cb36fb0b99f60825232655f5a989fc0bc6","tid":1830815,"uid":264965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:20:34.000Z","msg":"按共162個國家或地區於2017年的情況作評估"},{"pid":"14234acb51eecfa822760e900fd9ff076d7d6078","tid":1830815,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57cc75b6a6520690328923f27e5c04c376c381dc","tid":1830815,"uid":51677,"like":1